--[[
    Shaman UI Library
    Compact dark-grey UI library with:
    - Draggable + resizable window
    - Safe minimize / restore that clamps on screen
    - Close button
    - Global open / close keybind
    - Settings panel
    - Config save/load with visual restore
    - Animated collapsible sections
    - Global search across every tab
    - Accurate mouse hover dot
    - Tooltips
]]

